Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oui, you are the last to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo, something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, there's a face we don't see often.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone in need of punishment? I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've gathered us here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have called this meeting of the Supreme Five Swords\Nto discuss one matter of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy has entered our grounds. In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we must discuss how we will deal\Nwith this transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All the girls're armed to the teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's basically the same as all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He was expelled from his previous school\Nafter causing a brawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But his was on a much larger scale than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,More than forty people were seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no information on\Nwhat weapons he is skilled with,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but without a doubt, he is trained\Nin some kind of martial art.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I heard that he was\Nthe worst injured of all the victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and was only recently released from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If he did all that with his bare hands,\Nthat'd make him quite a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless, he's not our enemy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Warabi-chan! Lemme pet him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back! Your ways of loving animals\Nis much too self-serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Pay attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,His name's, uh... Nohmura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it with the accent on the first syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A cross-dressing dude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't crossdressing! It's makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you must be new here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, just never knew this school\Nhad its own giant Buddha statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have one, in the auditorium, gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One that looks a lot better than this, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then, Mister Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Masukodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There a lotta piggies like you runnin' around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That nickname's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Masukodera! Masukodera Kusuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, Masuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All the guys here are like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, weird school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but as long as I'm free to do what I want,\Ncouldn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Free to do what you want, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you do what the rest of us are doing,\Nthen you'll be granted the smallest bit of freedom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not into dressin' up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In either case, you'd better keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a guy who loves freedom and quiet\Nmore than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with all that crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My. It's a rare occasion for you to be\Ngracing us with your presence, Empress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I heard the name of an interesting man\Nbeing brought up, so I came to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please refrain from\Nacting as if you are above us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than feel this level of disgust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From what she's saying, it sounds like\Nshe's fought with this Nomura before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're gonna do it then, Kirukiru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That man will be joining my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the one to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll correct him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and his holier-than-thou attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be careful of his "magic bullets".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be an entertaining homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, could you wait just a few more moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, don't worry about it,\NI'm just gonna get there a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the hell is goin' on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.97,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,800)\pos(758.4,879.6)\blur1.5}Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.97,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,800)\pos(1384.8,879.6)\blur1.5}The Magnificent Blade, Onigawara Rin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Onigawara Rin, one of the Supreme Five Swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am here to correct your behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why's this happening all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like my teeth? Little late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you're not aware of your place in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no idea why you all got weapons,\Nor why the guys're wearin' makeup,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or what these Supreme Five swords are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you seriously don't know anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supreme Five Swords are the five girls\Nled by Rin who control the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aichi Coexistence Private Academy\Nused to be an all-girls school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it became a co-ed school,\Nthe girls were scared of the boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so they started arming them like a vigilante group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That custom has continued ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and five of those girls were\Ngiven permission to carry swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Their actions and successes led to the school becoming\Na place where delinquents were sent for reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Long story short, problem students\Nthat couldn't coexist in other schools
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,are brought here to be corrected\Nin the name of coexistence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(931.2,578.801)}Coexistence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(933.2,578.801)}Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why the Supreme Five Swords\Nstand atop all the armed girls here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is standard for the Five Swords\Nto correct a transfer student like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you finally get what I was saying this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one way to survive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw away your dignity as a man\Nand live as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the rest of us "girls."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave away their upper and lower fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like even an idiot like you\Ncan understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, sure, but look, I'm unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sayin' you're still gonna come at me\Nwith a bunch of weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm the only one who will be correcting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you trying to say that you would have been\Nable to take all of us if you were armed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be careful of his "magic bullets".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would like a weapon,\NI will have one procured for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, get me a megaphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shout for help real loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this is what they mean by\Na dog whose bark is worse than its bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, insult me all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I'd worried what he would be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like fighting someone\Nwho has no intention of baring his teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two options:\Ncoexist with the rest of us, or leave this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got my answer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like everything will end quietly,\Nwithout any bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free to do what I want, right?\NSo I'm sayin' no to both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You do know what this means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Japanese guy who knows how to say "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have no intention of coexisting. Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be easy to get outta here, but that'd be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't get a chance to get in\Nif I miss out on this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all here, might as well have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally show your fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But how exactly will you choose both options?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Before homeroom is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the bell rings, I, Onigawara Rin\Nwill correct your behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,'Scuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that glance to fake us out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free to go, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by the next bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you plan on literally running out the clock, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I finally understand why you ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a guy who loves freedom and quiet\Nmore than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves it way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't have both freedom\Nand quiet at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That rings especially true for us girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's chasing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How far are you going to make me chase you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it against school rules to leave the school grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Men of the academy must request permission\Nfrom the Five Swords to leave the grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you frickin' kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mozunono.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you open the window for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is a bit hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we get a good breeze coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't want a breeze, I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's mean! I just bought that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin Onee-sama is fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're still in homeroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just knock you off-balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(964.001,695.2)}Horizontal Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close! I almost lost my damn head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've got a strong, limber lower half.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your legs are not to be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, thanks, you're makin' me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm sure you have natural talent as well,\Nit's clear you've done your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Training, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't we stop fightin'\Nso we can talk about how great we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're swingin' around that sword\Nwith those tiny arms like it's nothin' is pretty charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I like a girl who's got muscle on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much muscle will hinder\Nyour ability to breathe properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the way of the\NKashima Shinden Jikishinkage school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirrored Breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.18,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(961.999,567.6)}Mirrored Breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jikishinkage school, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Onigawara is going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirrored Breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If a foreign object gets into the lungs, you will cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The body will use all of its muscles\Nto force the invading object out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Onigawara makes use of that reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With each breath, she focuses her will\Nto strengthen her immobilized core,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and by controlling it, she can draw forth power\Nsurpassing her physical abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Syncing the timing of her breathing and movements\Nleaves no openings in her attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No normal man could stand a chance\Nagainst Onigawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(944.8,656)}Dragon's Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, ya really got me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your frank honesty stands in contrast\Nto your shallow act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you're an earnest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you not, you wouldn't have\Nattained this much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that really makes me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(934.399,682)}Blur
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(925.601,642.4)}Chest Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going for my head or my nipples?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man, you don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I need 'em for nipple wrestling at New Year's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the champ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll give up your title this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(964.8,667.601)}Crane Stance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to take out her leg in front,\Nbut she jumped into that stance immediately after...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashima Shinden Jikishinkage school,\NHidden Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Carpenter's Square!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(961.999,636.8)}Carpenter's Square
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ability to see movement\Nhas become your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell for my technique because\Nyour rash judgment of distance was accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An eight-SUN sword, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do have some knowledge of swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll bring out my secret weapon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Blade-resistant gauntlets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Onihime's attacks can shatter bone\Njust by the shock of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid that, he's parrying her attacks\Nwith the back of his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to push her off with his palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How very amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard such a weird response\Nto roll call before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight's becoming a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't finish this quick,\NKirukiru is going to give us that cocky grin again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,222 seconds until homeroom is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(993.6,545.6)\blur1.5}Outer Rotation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(773.599,689.6)}Hidden Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(1360.001,689.6)\blur1.5}Cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to step back to keep breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's what you're waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you down before that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands can't hold out much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you fall forward because your posture wasn't right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In either case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I should praise you for being able to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's much too unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditch the sword and put your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have a sword, but I've got a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a failed secret sword technique\Nthat I made into my own special technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a name for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I guess I'd call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who told you that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off Rin Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?! It was an accident on my part!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Rin Onee-sama is-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,F-first, let's calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder isn't allowed on school grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, she's gonna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember, your name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I hadn't introduced myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The accent's on the "No".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Onigawara Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's trying real hard to say her catchphrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...will castrate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean "correct"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty different from the freedom and quiet\NI wanted in the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You must request permission from the Five Swords\Nto leave the school grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I've gotta get permission from
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the Five Swords to leave the grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer are you gonna run from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I've gotta get permission from\Nthe Five Swords to leave the grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Omugi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiko here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword techniques Onigawara Rin uses
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:30.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(948,681.199)\blur1.5}Horizontal Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:30.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(928.8,642)\blur1.5}Dragon's Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.18,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(940.399,670)}Blur
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,are from a school called the\NKashima Shinden Jikishinkage school!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Her special technique is her method of breathing\Nthat she calls Mirrored Breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:34.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1.5\pos(949.999,577.601)}Mirrored Breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathing certainly is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing it like that? Are you giving birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:40.89,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518.4,169.2)\b1\bord0\blur0.75}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:40.89,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(969.6,565.2)\b1\blur0.75\bord0}The Chastity Dorm Riot

